A 1960s vintage-style illustration of an elegant mahogany desk with an early computer terminal displaying glowing green text, surrounded by scattered paper carbon copies creating layered shadows, a brass desk lamp casting warm amber light, and an overflowing inbox tray with papers cascading like a waterfall. The scene is rendered in muted sepia tones with pops of teal and mustard yellow, featuring subtle halftone dot patterns and slightly faded edges reminiscent of mid-century magazine advertisements. A steaming coffee cup sits beside the terminal, and through a window, a retro cityscape with art deco buildings is visible against a dusky sky.
